sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant OS as OrderService (Subject)
    participant E as EmailObserver
    participant W as WarehouseObserver
    participant L as LoyaltyObserver
    participant K as KafkaObserver

    Note over OS: observers list = [E, W, L, K]

    C->>OS: placeOrder(order)
    OS->>OS: orderRepository.save(order)
    OS->>OS: publish(OrderPlacedEvent)

    OS->>E: onOrderPlaced(event)
    E->>E: emailService.sendConfirmation()

    OS->>W: onOrderPlaced(event)
    W->>W: warehouseService.notifyPacking()

    OS->>L: onOrderPlaced(event)
    L->>L: loyaltyService.awardPoints()

    OS->>K: onOrderPlaced(event)
    K->>K: kafkaTemplate.send("order-placed")

    Note over OS: Adding new observer = 1 class + 1 registerObserver()<br/>OrderService never changes
